Dialogue: 0,0:00:-06.-60,0:00:-03.-02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A world... Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:-03.00,0:00:00.-18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A world for you who seek freedom
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.-16,0:00:02.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,stretches out right before your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.01,0:00:06.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If your endless dreams are your guide,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.01,0:00:15.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,surpass them, under the flag of your beliefs!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.19,0:00:21.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Making a splash,\NI've just started on my search
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.69,0:00:26.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heading towards a world without end
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.20,0:00:31.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My heart bursting with enthusiasm,\NI'll go to the ends of the earth
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.37,0:00:39.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In search of light yet unseen
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.71,0:00:47.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When the summer sun\Nsways the sails of my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.82,0:00:57.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the cue to open the door to a new world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.33,0:01:04.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sailing through the rocky waves of despair
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.34,0:01:11.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We head beyond the horizon
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.01,0:01:17.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Making a splash,\NI've just started on my search
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.68,0:01:22.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heading towards a world without end
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.19,0:01:27.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My heart bursting with enthusiasm,\NI'll go to the ends of the earth
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.36,0:01:35.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In search of light yet unseen
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.26,0:01:38.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the insolent folks
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.59,0:01:46.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who didn't pay their taxes\Nat the harbor, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.20,0:01:52.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.20,0:01:57.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, what are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.21,0:02:05.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the Rainbow Mist!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.56,0:02:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Professor, where are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.22,0:02:14.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ape's Concert.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.23,0:02:16.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ape's Concert? It couldn't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.23,0:02:19.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.56,0:02:27.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A ship graveyard, where once\Nyou enter, you can never get out.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.24,0:02:35.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Residents of the Land of Eternity!\NThe Pumpkin Pirates!"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.53,0:02:51.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, look! There's nothing but\Nsunken ships, as far as you can see!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.20,0:02:55.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L-Let's give this up. It feels like a\Nghost captain might appear at any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.53,0:02:57.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? Ghost captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.87,0:02:59.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't call to them!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.54,0:03:02.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beyond the Rainbow Mist\Nis the world of the eternal.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.87,0:03:05.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The final paradise remaining on earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.54,0:03:07.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's filled with treasures of gold and silver,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.55,0:03:10.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,where people live forever\Nwithout aging or going hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.88,0:03:12.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what's written in this book.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.88,0:03:18.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, that's nothing more than a legend.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.22,0:03:22.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Professor, you knew that this\Nplace was a ship graveyard?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.56,0:03:27.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. 50 years ago, I got a\Nshort glimpse of this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.90,0:03:29.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you knew it, then why come?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.23,0:03:33.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you that, too.\NI've been carrying on my research
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.57,0:03:37.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in order to rescue my friends that\Nwere swallowed up in this mist.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.24,0:03:39.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I even became Wetton's dog,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.24,0:03:46.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and put up with the\Nfinger-pointing, to that end.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.85,0:03:48.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.85,0:03:56.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.86,0:03:59.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.20,0:04:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it awesome? There's lots,\Nlots more inside the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.54,0:04:05.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna go explore some more!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.87,0:04:08.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whether this is a paradise or not,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.21,0:04:10.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the "being filled with treasure"\Nthing doesn't appear to be
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.88,0:04:18.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,altogether untrue, huh, Professor?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.56,0:04:35.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those who would disturb\Nthe rest of the dead...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.90,0:04:37.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.57,0:04:41.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave the cargo, and depart at once,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.57,0:04:47.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or else, the curse of the dead shall befall you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.51,0:04:50.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm s-scared...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.18,0:04:54.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's there?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.85,0:05:00.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There they are!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.86,0:05:05.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, hand over the cargo, nice and easy...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.20,0:05:10.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or else...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.20,0:05:17.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was close! You rotten...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.88,0:05:25.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ghost captain...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.55,0:05:29.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.89,0:05:35.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're... ghosts... all... right...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.56,0:05:38.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that arrow came from over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.56,0:05:41.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.57,0:05:43.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy! Over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.90,0:05:47.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's someone over there!\NHey, listen to me, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.51,0:05:50.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy, I say!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.18,0:05:56.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, a bow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.18,0:06:02.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy! Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.85,0:06:05.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.36,0:06:11.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.86,0:06:19.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Special attack: Fire Star!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.88,0:06:27.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.55,0:06:31.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Akibi!\N--Wait, Rongo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.55,0:06:35.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Akibi!\N--Take it easy, Rongo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.55,0:06:38.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're just kids, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.89,0:06:41.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rongo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.56,0:06:43.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Akibi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.23,0:06:50.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot, stay away! Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.50,0:06:52.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.17,0:06:55.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I'm Home!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.84,0:06:57.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo, thank you for that earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.84,0:07:00.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.18,0:07:07.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rongo!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.19,0:07:13.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.19,0:07:17.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are the Pumpkin Pirates,\Nand Ape's Concert is our territory!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.86,0:07:22.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Release my friends, and turn over\Nthe cargo, if you want to live!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.87,0:07:24.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A bomb?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.20,0:07:26.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rapa Nui!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.87,0:07:28.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.54,0:07:32.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, now, if you use that, you'll blow us all up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.21,0:07:40.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're all in the same boat!\NWe live, and die, together!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.22,0:07:48.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Let's go.\N--I'm sorry, Rapa Nui. Rongo!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.49,0:07:53.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rapa Nui...? Is that you, Rapa Nui...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.17,0:07:59.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And... Isoka, and Rongo... It's you, all right...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.17,0:08:01.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you know me? It's me, Henzo!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.17,0:08:05.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We always used to play together,\Non Cape Luluka!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.51,0:08:06.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Henzo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.85,0:08:09.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know them?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.51,0:08:12.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Henzo? You don't mean that Henzo!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.85,0:08:15.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot, there's no way...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.85,0:08:20.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay back! I-I'll blow us up! Stay back, I said!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.19,0:08:28.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.54,0:08:35.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaboom Mark III. I invented it, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.87,0:08:43.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just a gizmo used for bluffing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.82,0:08:52.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, it's a smokescreen!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.49,0:08:55.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's all the racket...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.16,0:08:57.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're just now waking up?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.16,0:09:00.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? For that matter, who's the old guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.50,0:09:08.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it would take a bit of\Ntime to explain it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.51,0:09:15.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, they're gone from over here, too.\NWho was that just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.51,0:09:23.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh, Pops?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.22,0:09:58.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Henzo! Hurry on down!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.89,0:10:00.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm too scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.56,0:10:08.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be afraid over something\Nlike this! We're the Pumpkin Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.25,0:10:32.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I grow up, I'm gonna be a real pirate.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.26,0:10:35.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Rapa Nui, your father is a marine, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.59,0:10:37.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he going to let you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.60,0:10:39.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My pop is my pop.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.26,0:10:43.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to have adventures in places\Nthat nobody has seen before!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.27,0:10:45.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Places nobody has seen before?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.60,0:10:51.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure. There are still lots of things in\Nthis world that nobody knows about.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.54,0:10:53.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to see them, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.21,0:10:56.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me, too. I'll be a pirate, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.21,0:10:59.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we'll have to fight with\Nother pirates, too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.55,0:11:02.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone as weak as I am couldn't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.22,0:11:05.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Henzo, you can invent all\Nsorts of things, can't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.22,0:11:09.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll invent the gear that\Nwe'll need for our adventures.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.90,0:11:11.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.23,0:11:13.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'll be a pirate, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.90,0:11:21.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're easy to convince, Henzo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.24,0:11:28.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.25,0:11:31.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Playing as friends, and chatting...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.58,0:11:34.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I spent the best days of my life with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.92,0:11:42.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Every day was so bright,\Nit doesn't even compare to treasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.26,0:11:51.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until that one dreadful event occurred...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.88,0:12:07.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Henzo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.89,0:12:14.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Henzo! Are you all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.23,0:12:19.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've perfected the Kaboom Mark III!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.90,0:12:22.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot! Don't scare us like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.57,0:12:29.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure do have a lot of false alarms, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.57,0:12:32.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Holy crap! The town is on fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.58,0:12:40.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The town of Luluka is on fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.26,0:12:48.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What is this...?\N--Our town...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.53,0:12:51.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad! Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.86,0:12:59.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rongo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.88,0:13:05.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Burn! Burn!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.88,0:13:08.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave nothing of value!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.21,0:13:13.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kill everyone that opposes us,\Nthe Wetton Pirates! Got it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.89,0:13:21.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Show the women and children no mercy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.57,0:13:29.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.57,0:13:35.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this, there are still some kids\Nwho haven't run away, are there?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.57,0:13:39.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, guys, once we get to the harbor,\Nthere will be ships there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.24,0:13:42.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll take one of them, it doesn't\Nmatter which one, and get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.58,0:13:44.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what about Dad, and the others?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.58,0:13:46.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot! Do you wanna get killed?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.52,0:13:54.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.20,0:14:11.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those brats...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.88,0:14:18.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ships...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.88,0:14:22.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those guys earlier must have sunk them!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.89,0:14:24.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Over there! We'll get on that one!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.89,0:14:26.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? That one?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.22,0:14:34.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There aren't any others, right? Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.90,0:14:40.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing to my ship?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.57,0:14:48.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here he comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.18,0:14:56.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.86,0:15:04.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ker-splash!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.20,0:15:13.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You all are ready to answer for this, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.88,0:15:32.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry, up there!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.23,0:15:38.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think someone like you\Ncan handle this axe?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.23,0:15:41.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get too cocky, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.23,0:15:46.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not a kid! I'm Rapa Nui,\Nthe leader of the Pumpkin Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.84,0:15:49.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Rapa Nui!\N--It's all right! He's just one man!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.84,0:15:54.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's all join our forces together,\Nand defeat him!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.85,0:15:57.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Captain, are we setting sail already?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.52,0:16:05.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's another one!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.86,0:16:16.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Who are you guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.21,0:16:29.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.21,0:16:30.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Rainbow Mist!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.88,0:16:32.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hurry and turn the helm!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.55,0:16:35.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we get swallowed up inside there,\Nwe won't be able to get back!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.55,0:16:39.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The helm is busted!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.56,0:16:43.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you... You'll pay for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.23,0:16:44.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Akibi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.23,0:16:52.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't think you're getting\Nout of here alive anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.51,0:17:04.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Akibi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.18,0:17:05.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your shoulder's dislocated.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.85,0:17:09.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rapa Nui!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.19,0:17:17.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll pay for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.86,0:17:20.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Henzo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.87,0:17:23.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Henzo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.20,0:17:25.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go back! Turn the ship back!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.54,0:17:29.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't! The helm is busted!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.21,0:17:33.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Rainbow Mist... The Rainbow Mist...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.21,0:17:35.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rapa Nui!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.21,0:17:38.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go on! Keep going! Don't worry about me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.88,0:17:40.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Henzo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.22,0:17:42.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I promise, I'll come after you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.55,0:17:49.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am a member of the\NPumpkin Pirates, after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.49,0:17:56.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Henzo...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.17,0:17:59.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.17,0:18:04.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since, Rapa Nui and\Nthe others have never returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.51,0:18:09.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To think that they actually\Nbecame pirates in a place like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.18,0:18:12.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but that happened 50 years ago, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.85,0:18:16.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They were still just little kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.19,0:18:21.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The passage of time within the\NRainbow Mist appears to be different.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.53,0:18:24.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One day in here might be equivalent to a week,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.20,0:18:28.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or even a year, in the outside world.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.20,0:18:29.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.87,0:18:33.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's true, we have to\Nfind a way out of here fast,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.54,0:18:35.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or there'll be no undoing the damage.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.54,0:18:36.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.54,0:18:39.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are so dense!\NThe same thing that happened
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.21,0:18:42.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,between those kids earlier and the\Nold man could happen to us, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.55,0:18:44.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,While we're in here, puttering around,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.88,0:18:48.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami and the others we left behind\Nwill become old men and women!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.49,0:18:49.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.82,0:18:51.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Pops, let's go back, quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.82,0:18:55.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like he said, we don't know how to get back!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.49,0:18:58.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What?! Is that right?!\N--So, there's no way back?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.83,0:19:01.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What have you been listening to, Luffy?!\N--No... There must be a way
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.83,0:19:05.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--They must have said it... three times now!\N--to get out of Ape's Concert.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.17,0:19:12.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that many times?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.18,0:19:14.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, these guys are persistent.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.85,0:19:16.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That weapon is a real problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.85,0:19:24.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You shut your traps! I'll finish you off!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.53,0:19:38.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Lake-sama!\N--Are you all right, Lake-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.20,0:19:41.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you the ones who chucked that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.54,0:19:42.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, not us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.87,0:19:44.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For that matter, wasn't he watching?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.88,0:19:47.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is wearing that thing, and all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.55,0:19:50.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I asked you, was it you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.55,0:19:53.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What if we say it was?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.55,0:19:55.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.22,0:19:57.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're picking it up?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.56,0:20:01.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have collected your harbor dues.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.23,0:20:08.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I now formally welcome\Nyou as a citizen of Luluka.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.57,0:20:10.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ape's Concert, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.57,0:20:15.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Some soldiers said\Nthey saw your ship enter
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.24,0:20:18.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the Rainbow Mist, no doubt about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.24,0:20:24.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From what the mayor says, it's\Npiled up with treasure in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.25,0:20:25.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Treasure?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.92,0:20:29.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They say that Ape's Concert\Nis a ship graveyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.92,0:20:34.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The shipwrecks in there have\Nuntouched cargo all over the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.59,0:20:37.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The mayor is after that treasure,\Nwhich is why he has a scientist,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.60,0:20:41.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,named Henzo, researching a way\Nto get into Ape's Concert.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.27,0:20:44.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, the old man made\Nthis electroshock suit, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.94,0:20:48.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think? Pretty damn slick, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.54,0:20:51.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This guy sure likes to talk a lot, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.54,0:20:55.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shouldn't he be content\Nwith just getting the tax?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.21,0:20:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't just stand around here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.22,0:21:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going in into that mist, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.22,0:21:02.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir, Nami-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.22,0:21:04.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But once we go in there,\Nthere's no coming out!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.56,0:21:08.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What good will getting scared do?\NOur treasure is waiting for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.23,0:21:09.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.90,0:21:16.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one is allowed into Ape's Concert\Nwithout my permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.57,0:21:19.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Grandpa!\N--You bonehead!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.91,0:21:21.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa...?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.91,0:21:27.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got a poor memory.\NAren't I always telling you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.58,0:21:33.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are to call me "Mayor."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.92,0:21:40.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Mayor Wetton."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.20,0:21:48.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, beyond the never-ending sky
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.31,0:21:56.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The future that I once saw\Nis now starting to take shape
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.66,0:22:14.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are days where I almost lose to myself
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.17,0:22:22.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When that happened, there was\Nsomeplace warm I could go
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.55,0:22:28.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The friends I took pride in\Nalways, without fail,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.69,0:22:36.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,pushed me onwards, didn't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.70,0:22:47.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, the stars are pouring\Ndown underneath the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.97,0:22:55.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This unique moment...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.54,0:22:59.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you believe that the old man\Nand those kids were the same age?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.87,0:23:01.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what are you doing, Luffy?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.54,0:23:03.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was thinking that if we get the\Nship going, we can get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.21,0:23:04.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Should we be doing that without Nami?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.88,0:23:06.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's probably upset\Nabout being left behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.55,0:23:10.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She might be a wrinkly\Nold woman by now, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.22,0:23:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say anything so chilling!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.22,0:23:13.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.55,0:23:16.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Thoughts of Home!\NThe Pirate Graveyard of No Escape!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.89,0:23:24.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
